">:</span> orange<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>&#x3C;style>&#x3C;/style> 의 내용으로 스타일을 작성하는 방식이다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-인라인-방식\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%9D%B8%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B8-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\" aria-label=\"2 인라인 방식 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 인라인 방식</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> orange<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>요소의 style 속성에 직접 스타일을 작성하는 방식이다. (선택자 없음)<br />\n우선순위가 높아 유지보수에 악영향을 미치므로 사용이 권장되지 않는다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-링크-방식\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EB%A7%81%ED%81%AC-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\" aria-label=\"3 링크 방식 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 링크 방식</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>./css/main.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>&#x3C;link /> 로 외부 CSS 문서를 가져와서 연결하는 방식이다. (병렬 연결방식)</p>\n<h3 id=\"4-import-방식\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-import-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\" aria-label=\"4 import 방식 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. @import 방식</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@import</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">'./box.css'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> orange<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>CSS의 @import 규칙으로 CSS 문서 안에서<br />\n또 다른 CSS 문서를 가져와 연결하는 방식이다. (직렬 연결방식)</p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#-style-%EC%9D%98-%EC%84%A0%EC%96%B8-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D-%EB%84%A4%EA%B0%80%EC%A7%80\">💙 style 의 선언 방식 네가지</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-%EB%82%B4%EC%9E%A5-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\">1. 내장 방식</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-%EC%9D%B8%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B8-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\">2. 인라인 방식</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-%EB%A7%81%ED%81%AC-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\">3. 링크 방식</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#4-import-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\">4. @import 방식</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","excerpt":"💙 style 의 선언 방식 네가지 1. 내장 방식 <style></style> 의 내용으로 스타일을 작성하는 방식이다. 2. 인라인 방식 요소의 style 속성에 직접 스타일을 작성하는 방식이다. (선택자 없음)\n우선순위가 높아 유지보수에 악영향을 미치므로 사용이 권장되지 않는다. 3. 링크 방식 <link /> 로 외부 CSS 문서를 가져와서 연결하는 방식이다. (병렬 연결방식) 4. @import 방식 CSS의 @import 규칙으로 CSS 문서 안에서\n또 다른 CSS 문서를 가져와 연결하는 방식이다. (직렬 연결방식) 💙 style 의 선언 방식 네가지 1. 내장 방식 2. 인라인 방식 3. 링크 방식 4. @import 방식","frontmatter":{"date":"2022.03.09","title":"[CSS] 스타일 선언 방식","categories":"CSS","author":"안가을","emoji":null},"fields":{"slug":"/css/add-style/"}},"next":{"id":"5adf85a5-13e7-55c6-b48d-9707e4a8d31f","html":"<h2 id=\"-전역-속성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%AD-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\" 전역 속성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💙 전역 속성</h2>\n<p>HTML 에서 속성이란<br />\n열리는 태그에 작성하는 href, target, src 같은 HTML 의 기능을 확장해주는 개념이다.<br /></p>\n<p>기본적으로 요소들은 자신이 <strong>사용할 수 있는 속성이 정해져 있다.</strong> (img태그: src, a태그: href 등)<br />\n하지만 <strong>전역 속성</strong>은 body 에서 사용하는 태그들의 전체 영역에서 언제든지 사용할 수 있다.<br /></p>\n<h3 id=\"1title\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1title\" aria-label=\"1title permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.title</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://naver.com<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">target</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>_blank<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>네이버로 이동<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>NAVER<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>요소의 <strong>정보</strong>나 <strong>설명</strong>을 지정한다.<br />\n해당 요소에 마우스를 올리면 일종의 tooltip 처럼 title 속성이 출력된다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-style\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-style\" aria-label=\"2 style permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. style</h3>\n<p>요소에 적용할 <strong>스타일</strong>을 지정한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-class\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-class\" aria-label=\"3 class permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. class</h3>\n<p>요소를 지칭하는 <strong>중복 가능</strong>한 이름이다.<br />\ncss, js 에서 해당 요소를 제어하기 위해서 사용한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"4-id\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-id\" aria-label=\"4 id permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. id</h3>\n<p>요소를 지칭하는 <strong>중복이 불가능</strong>한 고유한 이름이다.<br />\n자주 사용하지는 않지만, 중요한 위치에 이름을 부여할 때에는 id 를 사용하는 것이 효율적이다.<br />\n해당하는 요소를 빠르게 찾아서 제어할 수 있기 때문이다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"5-data\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-data\" aria-label=\"5 data permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. data</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-cute-animal</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>cat<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>고양이<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-cute-animal</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>dog<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>강아지<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>&#x3C;div <strong>data-이름=“데이터”</strong>>&#x3C;/div> 형태로 사용하며,<br />\n요소에 <strong>데이터</strong>를 지정할 수있다.</p>\n<br />\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> items <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelectorAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'div'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n